<section class="features-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <h2 class="section-title">Powerful features for pros</h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle">Everything you need to create, optimize, and manage your App Store presence</p>
    </div>

    <div class="features-grid">
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path d="M12 2L2 7l10 5 10-5-10-5z"/>
            <path d="m2 17 10 5 10-5"/>
            <path d="m2 12 10 5 10-5"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Element layers</h3>
        <p>Organize your screenshots with powerful layering system. Move, resize, and style elements independently for pixel-perfect control.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <circle cx="11" cy="11" r="8"/>
            <path d="m21 21-4.35-4.35"/>
            <circle cx="11" cy="11" r="3"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Loupe effect</h3>
        <p>Highlight specific UI elements with our signature loupe magnification. Perfect for showcasing detailed features and interactions.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path d="M21 15V6"/>
            <path d="M18.5 18a2.5 2.5 0 1 0 0-5 2.5 2.5 0 0 0 0 5Z"/>
            <path d="M12 12H3"/>
            <path d="M16 6H3"/>
            <path d="M12 18H3"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>XCStrings integration</h3>
        <p>Import and export Xcode localization files seamlessly. Keep your screenshots in sync with your app's localization workflow.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path d="M16 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/>
            <circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/>
            <path d="m22 21-3-3"/>
            <path d="m15 12 3 3"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Variant management</h3>
        <p>Create unlimited variations without touching originals. Perfect for A/B testing different messaging, colors, and layouts.</p>
      </div>


      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path d="M4 7v10c0 2.21 5.07 4 8 4s8-1.79 8-4V7M4 7c0 2.21 5.07 4 8 4s8-1.79 8-4M4 7c0-2.21 5.07-4 8-4s8 1.79 8 4"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Custom overlays</h3>
        <p>Add images, text, shapes, and custom elements on top of your screenshots. Perfect for highlighting features and adding marketing copy.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path d="M14 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V8z"/>
            <polyline points="14,2 14,8 20,8"/>
            <line x1="16" y1="13" x2="8" y2="13"/>
            <line x1="16" y1="17" x2="8" y2="17"/>
            <polyline points="10,9 9,9 8,9"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Text styling with markdown</h3>
        <p>Style your text with powerful markdown support. Create bold, italic, highlighted text with background colors and custom formatting.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path d="M14.5 10a4.5 4.5 0 0 0 4.5 4.5M14.5 10a4.5 4.5 0 0 1-4.5 4.5M14.5 10L2 2v20l12.5-8z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Upload to App Store A/B tests</h3>
        <p>Directly upload your screenshot variants to App Store Connect for A/B testing. Compare performance and optimize conversion rates.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <rect x="16" y="16" width="6" height="6" rx="1"/>
            <rect x="2" y="16" width="6" height="6" rx="1"/>
            <rect x="9" y="2" width="6" height="6" rx="1"/>
            <path d="m5 16-3-3h18l-3 3"/>
            <path d="M12 12V8"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Preview variants & localizations</h3>
        <p>Preview all your screenshot variants and localizations side by side. Compare different versions before publishing to ensure quality.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <rect width="18" height="18" x="3" y="3" rx="2"/>
            <path d="M9 9h6v6H9V9z"/>
            <path d="m16 3-3 3-3-3"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Background images</h3>
        <p>Use custom background images to create stunning visual contexts for your app screenshots. Upload your own or choose from templates.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <rect width="16" height="20" x="4" y="2" rx="2" ry="2"/>
            <line x1="12" y1="18" x2="12.01" y2="18"/>
            <rect width="20" height="16" x="2" y="4" rx="2" ry="2"/>
            <circle cx="8" cy="8" r="2"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Real & custom device bezels</h3>
        <p>Choose from real device bezels or create custom bordered designs. Support for iPhone, iPad, Mac, and Apple Watch frames.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path d="M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Theming system</h3>
        <p>Create and save custom themes to maintain consistency across all your screenshots. Apply brand colors, fonts, and styles instantly.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path d="M17 2.1l4 4-4 4"/>
            <path d="M3 12.2l4 4 4-4"/>
            <rect x="5" y="6" width="14" height="8" rx="2"/>
            <rect x="7" y="8" width="6" height="4" rx="1"/>
            <circle cx="18" cy="8" r="1"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Multi-device support</h3>
        <p>Create screenshots for iPhone, iPad, Mac, and Apple Watch. One tool for all your Apple ecosystem app marketing needs.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .features-section {
    padding: 6rem 0;
    background: white;
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 1rem;
  }

  .section-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
  }

  .section-title {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #111827;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.1;
  }

  .section-subtitle {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    color: #6b7280;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .features-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .feature-card {
    background: #fafbfc;
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 2rem;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    border: 1px solid transparent;
  }

  .feature-card:hover {
    background: white;
    border-color: #e5e7eb;
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
  }

  .feature-icon {
    width: 48px;
    height: 48px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
    border-radius: 12px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: white;
  }

  .feature-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #111827;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .feature-card p {
    color: #6b7280;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .section-title {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }

    .features-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 1.5rem;
    }

    .feature-card {
      padding: 1.5rem;
    }
  }
</style>